```json
{
  "application": "OpenFOAM",
  "software_requirements": [
    "gcc/10.2.0",
    "openmpi",
    "cmake",
    "boost",
    "vtk",
    "nvhpc",
    "cuda",
    "conda",
    "OpenFOAM",
    "nsys"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "account": "bddir15",
    "time": "2:0:0",
    "partition": "gpu",
    "nodes": 1,
    "gres": "gpu:2",
    "email": "<your.email>@brunel.ac.uk"
  },
  "other_details": {
    "run_functions": "source $WM_PROJECT_DIR/bin/tools/RunFunctions",
    "parallel_execution": "foamDictionary system/decomposeParDict -entry numberOfSubdomains -set 16",
    "hierarchical_decomposition": "foamDictionary system/decomposeParDict -entry hierarchicalCoeffs/n -set \"( 4 4 1 )\"",
    "blockMeshDict_modification": "sed -i 's/(400 400 1)/(4000 4000 1)/g' system/blockMeshDict",
    "nvidia_smi_log": "nvidia-smi > log.nvidia-smi",
    "pre_processing": "./Allrun.pre",
    "profiling": "nsys profile -t nvtx,cuda -o report_cpu -f true --stats=true /nobackup/projects/bddir15/hpc_sdk/Linux_ppc64le/23.1/comm_libs/mpi/bin/mpirun -n $nProcs $FOAM_USER_APPBIN/$application -parallel > log.$application 2>&1",
    "reconstruction": "runApplication reconstructPar",
    "post_processing": "./Allpost"
  }
}
```
